reviews.review_text: Best version of this trippy concert. i had the good fortune of attending this amazing show but never really found a recording that did the performance full justice. Unfortunately Bob Weir's guitar is almost non-existent ion the sbd..But this excellent audience recording capture the whole performance brilliantly.
